replyContent: Hi Landon, the small balance that is leftover in your wallet is known as dust. Dust occurs when the amount left in your wallet can't cover the blockchain network fee as well as the fee for selling that crypto. You have four options to manage dust, learn more by contacting us here: https://help.coinbase.com/en/contact-us
